      "bodyText": "SYNAPSE\nYour Knowledge Operating System\nHome\nSearch\nSettings\nMACRO-GALAXY\nDavid's Knowledge Operating System\n\nHome is now a real surface: browse the galaxy index on the left, keep personal modules on the canvas, and teleport straight into any node without drowning in admin chrome.\n\nGALAXIES\n5\nTOTAL NODES\n13\nAVERAGE MASTERY\n14%\nWORMHOLES\n1\nAdd Galaxy\nAdd Home Module\nSettings\nCheck Updates\nGalaxy Index\n\nTreat the nested file structure like a first-class navigator, not hidden plumbing.\n\n1/13 complete\nAcademics\n2\nAcademic\n0%\n0 direct surfaces • 0 nested nodes\nAcademics\n12%\n1 direct surfaces • 7 nested nodes\nHealth\n1\nHealth\n50%\n1 direct surfaces • 2 nested nodes\nProjects\n2\nCode Repos\n0%\n1 direct surfaces • 2 nested nodes\nPersonal Projects\n0%\n1 direct surfaces • 2 nested nodes\nRecent Teleports\n\nResume a node instantly from the home stage.\n\nSearch All\nAcademics\nAcademics\n16 Mar 2026\nAcademic\nAcademic\n16 Mar 2026\nCode Repos\nCode Repos\n16 Mar 2026\nTraining\nHealth\n16 Mar 2026\nHealth\nHealth\n16 Mar 2026\nWeek 12 Split\nHealth\n16 Mar 2026\nHome Modules\n\nKeep your launchpad personal: notes, high-level analytics, shortcuts, and custom widgets all live here now.\n\nAdd Module\nSpatial Canvas\nDrag cards ",
